<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="KR3b0003-zh-0dd154ac" type="transl"><teiHeader><fileDesc><titleStmt><title>孫子今注今譯</title><editor role="translator">Wu Rulin 吳汝林</editor></titleStmt><publicationStmt><ab>published electronically as part of the TLS project at https://hxwd.org</ab><availability status="4">The copyright status of this work is unclear</availability></publicationStmt><sourceDesc><bibl><title>孫子今注今譯</title>臺北：商務印書館，1972</bibl><ab>Translation of <bibl corresp="#KR3b0003"><title xml:lang="och">孫子</title></bibl> into <lang xml:lang="zh">Chinese</lang>.</ab></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><creation resp="#CH">Initially created: <date>2024-05-10T16:37:08.814+09:00</date> by CH</creation></profileDesc></teiHeader><text><body><div><head>Translated parts</head><p xml:id="KR3b0003-start"><seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-1a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-10T16:37:54.45+09:00">孫子說：·</seg><seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-1a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-10T16:38:32.161+09:00">戰爭</seg><seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-1a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-10T16:38:35.305+09:00">是國家的大事，</seg><seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-1a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-10T16:38:45.292+09:00">關係人民生死，</seg><seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-1a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-10T16:38:51.582+09:00">國家存亡，</seg><seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-1a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-10T16:38:54.209+09:00">是不可不細心研究和慎重考慮的</seg><seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-10T16:39:51.117+09:00">所以要從五方面來，</seg><seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-10T16:39:59.742+09:00">比較，核算，</seg><seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-10T16:40:09.738+09:00">探求其事實。</seg><seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-10T16:40:17.02+09:00">第一是主義，</seg><seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-10T16:40:20.425+09:00">第二是時間，</seg><seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-10T16:40:24.551+09:00">第三是空閒，</seg><seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-10T16:40:34.081+09:00">第四是精神，</seg><seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-10T16:41:17.325+09:00">第五是紀律。</seg><seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-10T16:42:04.241+09:00">道的含義，</seg><seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-10T16:42:31.796+09:00">就是使全國人民，意志統一，</seg><seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-10T16:43:04.802+09:00">精砷集中，人民和政府，</seg><seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-10T16:43:13.475+09:00">才能同心協力、同生死，</seg><seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-10T16:43:21.33+09:00">共疊而不怕犧牲。</seg><seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-10T16:43:53.033+09:00">天，</seg><seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-10T16:44:02.472+09:00">就是指晝夜，晴雨，晦明，寒暑，時間的限制力與機動力等而言。</seg><seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-10T16:45:35.978+09:00">地，</seg><seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-10T16:45:57.214+09:00">為將者，</seg><seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-10T16:45:42.267+09:00">就是指道途的遠近，地形的險易與廣狹，生死的全般情勢等是。</seg><seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-10T16:46:30.027+09:00">必須具有才智，威信，仁愛，英勇，嚴肅等精砷與性格。</seg><seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.21" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-10T16:46:38.488+09:00">法，</seg><seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.22" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-10T16:47:14.351+09:00">就是指編制(組織制度)．人事(紀律賞罰)，主計(經理財務）而言。</seg><seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.23" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-10T16:47:52.401+09:00">這五方面的情事，</seg><seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.24" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-10T16:48:11.5+09:00">作軍官的，都不能不深入了解，</seg><seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.25" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-10T16:48:23.602+09:00">能正確了解的，便能打勝仗｀</seg><seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.26" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-10T16:50:02.605+09:00">不能正確了解的，</seg><seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.27" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-10T16:50:03.921+09:00">便不能打勝仗。</seg><seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.28" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-10T16:50:20.329+09:00">所以從各方面來，</seg><seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.29" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-10T16:50:47.977+09:00">比較，核算，</seg><seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.30" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-10T16:51:32.947+09:00">誰的法令，</seg><seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.31" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-10T16:51:42.82+09:00">能貫澈實行？</seg><seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.32" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-10T16:51:57.728+09:00">誰旳軍賒強大？</seg><seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.33" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-10T16:52:20.694+09:00">誰的士兵有探求共事實，</seg><seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.35" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-10T16:54:21.209+09:00">誰的將領具有才能？</seg><seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.34" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-10T16:54:17.641+09:00">然後自問：誰的主帥，能使全體軍民意志統一與精轉集中？</seg><seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.36" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-10T17:01:01.256+09:00">誰的士兵有訓練？誰的賞罰，公正嚴明？誰得天時與地利？誰的法令，能貫澈實行？誰旳軍賒強大？</seg><seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.37" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-10T16:59:25.849+09:00">根據這些事實判斷，便能預先知道誰勝誰敗了</seg></p></div></body></text></TEI>